{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Slots API",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "Slots RGS (Remote Game Server) API.\n\n**Auth flow (two-token pattern):**\n1. `POST /api/v1/auth/register` or `/login` — returns a 15-min **access token** in the body; sets a 7-day **refresh token** in an `httpOnly` cookie\n2. Copy `access_token` → click **Authorize** → paste → game endpoints unlock\n3. When the access token expires, `POST /api/v1/auth/refresh` silently issues a new pair (token rotation)\n4. `POST /api/v1/auth/logout` revokes all refresh tokens and clears the cookie"
  },
