        ],
        "summary": "Register a new player account",
        "description": "Creates an account and issues a token pair:\n- **Body**: 15-min RS256 access token — copy and paste into **Authorize**\n- **Cookie** (`httpOnly`): 7-day refresh token — stored by the browser, never readable by JS",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
